        "---\n",
        "title: \"Community-Generated Lesson: Mapping Wildfire Burned Areas Using VIIRS/AVIRIS-3 Data (Python)\"\n",
        "author: \n",
        "  - \"David Fonseca\"\n",
        "format: \n",
